  "description": {
   "en": "Behind World War II, the war that shook the entire human race, there was a history that was never depicted! Those who lost their loved ones and reached the depths of despair gained a different ability - the Rebellion. After the attack on Pearl Harbor, Genji is interned in an American internment camp for Japanese Americans, where he is kept in solitary confinement for fear of his unique ability of immortality. On the fateful day, a messenger from the president named Grossman comes to visit him. After the tragedy of that day, Genji begins his path as a rebel = Rebellion...!",
   "ja": "第二次世界大戦、全人類を揺るがせた戦争の裏には、決して描かれることのない歴史があった!! 大切な人を失い、絶望の淵に達することで、異能を手にした者たち──レベリオン。真珠湾襲撃後、アメリカの日系人収容所に収容されたゲンジは、不死という異能を恐れられ、独房に封じ込められる。運命の日、グロスマンなる大統領からの使者が来訪する。その日の惨劇から、ゲンジは反逆者＝レベリオンとしての道を歩み始める‥‥!!"
  },
